<div class="p">
    <strong><a target="_blank" href="~/public/perfViewer.js">perfViewer.js</a></strong> is a script to effortlessly display performance metrics on any page.
    When the script is initialized, it shows a notification bar with the page load time and a link to display a waterfall chart.
    All of this is done in JavaScript based on the HTML5 navigation and resource timings API.
</div>

