<h2>Integrating perfViewer</h2>
<p>To use perfViewer.js on your website, simply add it to your page and initialize it from a window load event handler.  For example:</p>
<pre class="code">&lt;script src=&quot;scripts/perfViewer.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;
    window.addEventListener('load', function() { perfViewer.init(); }, false);
&lt;/script&gt;
</pre>

